<p>He is also favorite to spin at corporate company events to provide entertainment for employees celebrating a company&#8217;s progress or success. Playing dance music and working in the past with big brand name like Intel, KPMG, Banana Republic, Essence of Australia, and Staub Electronics of Canada.</p>

<p>DJ Misha offers the services listed below for hire in the San Diego area and around the world. Traveling in the past to Hawaii, Kansas City, San Francisco areas to perform with <a href="/dj-saxophone/">saxophone player</a> Jason Whitmore playing along with the DJs music. Please contact Misha by phone or text about any questions you may have &#8211; to inquire about your event date or begin the booking process.</p>

