<p>Light up the excitement at any event by adding a live Saxophone accompaniment to play along the dance beats of the DJ. It's fun, exciting and always a top hit among guest. Saxophone player Jason Whitmore has been playing with DJ Misha since 2007. Learn more about the way they entertain together.</p>

